    v2 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.66) / (v1 + 0.79 + v2 + 0.14)) - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.80) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.65)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = (0.83 / 0.16)
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.sin(v1))
